file.name: schemas.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.1"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger Petstore
paths:
  /pets:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: some response
          content:
            'application/json':
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pet'
    post:
      responses:
        '201':
          description: creation ok
          content:
            'application/json':
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pet'
components:
  schemas:
    Pet:
      type: object
